Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.34,0:22:31.52,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「諦め」がくれた安楽  沈滞の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:34.45,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつからだっただろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:37.71,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ふいに輝き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.71,0:22:40.96,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わらずにいてと願うこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.00,0:22:44.57,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}変わりゆく時に生きる僕ら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:46.22,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}本当の声を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:47.80,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}言い得ぬ夢を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:50.22,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と繋がった空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:52.02,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}響かせて！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.89,0:22:55.99,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もっと強く…この両手で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.15,0:22:59.32,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}涙全て振り払えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:02.71,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「今度こそは…」つぶやく今と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:05.92,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷さえも無駄にしない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:09.28,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もっと早く…君のもとへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:12.46,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}たとえ羽が千切れようとも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:15.88,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歪む世界走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:19.00,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}感覚のその向うへ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:24.56,lrc_JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}「真実」と 加速してく
Comment: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------TXT----------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加速…了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3D影像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙一副嚇得腿軟的樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他的名字也沒印象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他是金屬色  多少有點能耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不是NPC而是人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是超頻連線者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(330,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是久違的世紀末場地  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手還是個亮閃閃的菜鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超幸運的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  你卻是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒大楣了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該不會是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏得了就有鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就被人逮到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點以為自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為你沒履行好和我的約定  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一不留神接上全球網路是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就可以省下口頭說明了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你已經發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain  Burst這款程式是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一款單純的對戰格鬥遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是以現實世界為舞台的遭遇戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真夠誇張的
